          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1616514183272-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a dry, large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat</p><p>Add the <strong>pork belly strips </strong>to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 8 min on each side or until golden and crispy</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1616514189364-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1616514189364-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1616514189364-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1616514189364-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1616514189364-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, transfer the <strong>crispy pork belly strips</strong> to <strong>kitchen paper</strong> and remove the pan from the heat</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced garlic</strong> to the pan and cook for 2-3 min or until golden</p><p>Tip: The pan should be hot enough to cook the garlic in already!</p><p>Slice the <strong>pork belly strips</strong> into small bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1616514195099-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1616514195099-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1616514195099-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1616514195099-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1616514195099-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>lettuce leaves</strong>, <strong>sticky rice</strong>, <strong>crispy pork belly strips</strong>, <strong>samjang</strong>, <strong>garlic</strong> and <strong>sliced spring onion </strong>in the middle of the table to serve</p><p>To eat, spread a <strong>lettuce leaf</strong> with some <strong>samjang</strong> and top with a spoonful of <strong>cooked rice</strong>,<strong> crispy pork belly</strong>, <strong>sliced garlic</strong> and <strong>spring onion</strong></p><p>Fold them up into a wrap and enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
